{"tid":1598273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美屬香港，一切由空想開始","createTime":"2019-09-27T11:06:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T19:52:36.000Z","uid":267881,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"623c89b1e7fbfba02aba1120e90317ee6c2b3528","tid":1598273,"uid":267881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:06:02.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\">藍絲廢老港豬驚攬炒？<br />\n建制走狗驚清算？<br />\n示威者破壞香港經濟？<br />\n香港鬥唔過共產黨？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">如果俾呢樣嘢你呢？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.vietnamimmigration.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/10/Vietnam-visa-for-citizens-of-Guam-1024x680.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vietnamimmigration.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2012%2F10%2FVietnam-visa-for-citizens-of-Guam-1024x680.jpg&h=e59e6190&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />參考返美屬關島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關島人出生即為美國公民<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />官方語言 英語 查莫羅語<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關島總督為民選產生<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關島立法會以不分區方式普選<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />關島政黨有民主黨和共和黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />收入主要依靠旅遊業和美軍開支<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img sr